  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/64d3d99178960f71a3cb28bbb1a48448.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br><strong>Add the game Delivery Boy to the wishlist and you will be the first to know about its release on Steam!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/8bd2298253645418d39f30d819249196.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br>Play as a budding courier who has moved to Crystal City in search of work. Before you is a city of great opportunities, help the main character climb the career ladder and become the best courier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/8fa845794cf2a8db39356f477b23ca7e.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br>■ Take various orders, deliver them to the right place and get money and experience points.<br>■ Open and manage delivery services.<br>■ Upgrade your own home and make it the prettiest in town!<br>■ Use special devices such as a resource detector, a garbage collector, and even a gravity gun to lift especially heavy loads.<br>■ Collect collectibles hidden throughout the city and explore interesting places.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/c54e2578f47d25b27eeca2a236ced424.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br>The game is being developed by indie developer Sergey Poroshin. Thanks for your support!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/64d3d99178960f71a3cb28bbb1a48448.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br><strong>Add the game Delivery Boy to the wishlist and you will be the first to know about its release on Steam!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/8bd2298253645418d39f30d819249196.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br>Play as a budding courier who has moved to Crystal City in search of work. Before you is a city of great opportunities, help the main character climb the career ladder and become the best courier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/8fa845794cf2a8db39356f477b23ca7e.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br>■ Take various orders, deliver them to the right place and get money and experience points.<br>■ Open and manage delivery services.<br>■ Upgrade your own home and make it the prettiest in town!<br>■ Use special devices such as a resource detector, a garbage collector, and even a gravity gun to lift especially heavy loads.<br>■ Collect collectibles hidden throughout the city and explore interesting places.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1550560/extras/c54e2578f47d25b27eeca2a236ced424.avif?t=1708518914\" width=590 height=116 /></span><br><br>The game is being developed by indie developer Sergey Poroshin. Thanks for your support!",
